                            <comment id="13020404" author="rhillegas" created="Fri, 15 Apr 2011 20:22:35 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;The description on the web site appears to be copied out of the header comment on LogToFile. That header comment should be updated too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13020499" author="bryanpendleton" created="Sat, 16 Apr 2011 01:08:14 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This sounds like it might be a reasonable &quot;newcomer&quot; task, or a reasonable GSoC task?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13020993" author="rhillegas" created="Mon, 18 Apr 2011 13:16:19 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Bryan, that&apos;s a good suggestion. I have marked this issue for Newcomers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13845503" author="myrna" created="Wed, 11 Dec 2013 16:14:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has not gotten picked up in GSoC sessions, and I was looking at &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5195&quot; title=&quot;Create tools for browsing the files in the database log directory.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-5195&quot;&gt;DERBY-5195&lt;/a&gt;, so I thought I&apos;d look at this. Attaching patches for the header in LogToFile and the web.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
